Function reference

Graph components

add_e61_logo()
Add e61 Logo to graph
add_zeroline()
Adds a black line at y = 0
labs_e61()
Wrapper function to produce e61 style graph footers
plot_label()
Add On-graph Labels to Graphs
mplot_label()
Add Multiple On-graph Labels to Graphs

Formatting

format_flip_bar_charts()
Applies changes to the theme for horizontal bar graphs
e61_palette()
Create e61 colour palette
square_legend_symbols()
Converts all legend colours to squares
theme_e61()
e61 themed graph options
theme_e61_clean()
e61 themed graph options in a 'clean' style
save_e61()
Saves ggplot graphs with sensible defaults

Scales

scale_y_continuous_e61() scale_x_continuous_e61()
Format axes in the e61 Institute style
scale_colour_e61() scale_fill_e61()
Set e61 colour palettes in scale_*_manual/gradient
scale_colour_e61_aus() scale_fill_e61_aus()
A consistent set of colours for Australian states and territories for graphing

Miscellaneous

crop_aus_coord()
Crops maps of Australia to exclude outlying territories
e61_map()
Wrapper function for ggmap to produce a map layer in e61 format
